  ('gsoc-gnome-mutter-overlay-planes', 'GNOME — Overlay-plane Unredirection in mutter', 'Teach Mutter to scan-out client buffers directly to DRM overlay planes — bypassing the GL composite path for full-screen video or fullscreen games. Saves significant GPU power on laptops and reduces latency.', 'Build mutter from gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/mutter using meson plus the gnome-build-meta jhbuild profile. Read src/backends/native/meta-kms-impl-device-atomic.c and the existing primary-plane scan-out path.

