  ('gsoc-joomla-frontend-editing', 'Joomla — Unified Front-end Editing Experience', 'Reconcile the inconsistent inline-editing experiences across Joomla core components — Articles, Modules, Menus — into a single workflow that respects ACL and the Workflow system. Touches PHP services, REST endpoints and Vue-flavoured layouts.', 'Fork github.com/joomla/joomla-cms and run `composer install && npm ci && npm run build` to get a dev site running. The relevant code paths are administrator/components/com_content and components/com_content/src/View/Article.

