  ('gsoc-aossie-eduaid-quiz', 'AOSSIE — EduAid Browser Extension for Auto Quiz Generation', 'Build a Chromium and Firefox WebExtension that turns any web article into a study quiz using transformer-based question-generation pipelines. Output ships back into the AOSSIE learning-tools stack.', 'Read github.com/AOSSIE-Org/EduAid — the manifest v3 skeleton is already there. The QG backend lives in github.com/AOSSIE-Org/Doc2Quiz; it uses HuggingFace transformers around the t5-base model.

