  ('gsoc-organicmaps-wikipedia-rust', 'Organic Maps — Wikipedia Dump Parser in Rust', 'Rewrite Organic Maps Wikipedia importer in Rust so the entire planet wiki dump can be parsed in hours, not days, producing the per-language summaries the app ships offline. Replaces a slow legacy pipeline.', 'Read github.com/organicmaps/organicmaps/tree/master/tools/python/descriptions to see the current pipeline. The Wikipedia multistream dump format is documented at en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Database_download.

