  ('gsoc-fossi-moore-hdl-compiler', 'FOSSi Foundation — Push Real-world Designs Through Moore HDL', 'Bring the Rust-based Moore SystemVerilog compiler closer to elaborating real industrial cores like Ibex and CVA6. Work includes filling parser gaps, fixing elaboration bugs and improving error messages.', 'Read github.com/fabianschuiki/moore — the architecture overview in README.md explains how the AST, HIR and MIR layers fit together. Build with `cargo build` and run `moore --help`.

