  ('gsoc-fortran-stdlib-sparse', 'Fortran-Lang — Sparse Matrix API for stdlib', 'Design and implement the COO and CSR sparse matrix formats in fortran-lang/stdlib together with the matrix-vector kernels needed by scientific simulations. Keeps performance comparable to handwritten code with no allocation in inner loops.', 'Clone github.com/fortran-lang/stdlib, follow CONTRIBUTING.md and run `cmake -B build && cmake --build build && ctest`. Read existing modules src/stdlib_linalg.* for naming and IO conventions.

