  ('gsoc-gimp-color-ocio', 'GIMP — OpenColorIO Color Management Integration', 'Add an OpenColorIO display and view-transform pipeline to GIMP 3, so VFX and color-graded workflows can render with ACEScg, Rec.709 and custom OCIO configs alongside the existing ICC profile path.', 'Build GIMP from gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/gimp following the README and pick up OpenColorIOs C++ API from opencolorio.org. The existing color management code lives in app/operations/gimpoperationcolormanagementmixin.* and libgimpcolor.

