  ('gsoc-owasp-juiceshop-web3', 'OWASP Juice Shop — Web3 Smart-contract Challenges', 'Add a new challenge category that teaches Solidity vulnerabilities — reentrancy, integer overflow, signature replay — inside the existing OWASP Juice Shop CTF framework. Players exploit on-chain contracts hosted on a local Hardhat node.', 'Fork github.com/juice-shop/juice-shop and read data/static/challenges.yml plus frontend/src/app/Services/challenge.service.ts to learn how challenges are scored. Spin up github.com/juice-shop/juicy-chat-bot to see how new modules are integrated.

